In the interview, David describes his two-week ordeal with COVID-19 and urges other young men to heed the public health warnings.
One of my friends had a baby shower, but Latin baby showers are just more excuses to throw a big party.
I remember being really, really scared, not knowing what was going on.
I started feeling, probably day one, fever, chills, fatigue, muscle and body aches, complete loss of appetite, no desire to do anything, just staying in my bed most of the day.
Look for the episode “A COVID-19 Survivor Warns Other Men.”